chunkSaveDelay.desc:: Delay before a chunk is saved to disk, default: 300 seconds

chunkUnloadLimit.desc:: Maximum amount of chunks unloaded per tick, default: 20, vanilla:200

disableProtoSave.desc:: Disables saving of protochunks(not fully generated chunks) to reduce saving lag. Default: true

debugLogging.desc:: Enables debug logging of how many chunks got saved in a tick. default: false
